description: Greetings friends and fans of the Jehovah Shalom Acapella UG. Did you know? We have a new and amazing song already out? Yes.!! Situka Okole. With the message to emphasize the need to work and trust in the Lord the source of it all. This is us, this is what we live for, to live to serve, teach and inspire. If you haven't heard it already feel free to inbox your contact and in a snap twill on your mobile. #SitukaOkole
